what does the term nice guys finish last mean it goes back to baseball manager leo durocher a sportswriter asked him if he thought a person with another team was a nice guy nice guys finish last was his reply it means do whatever you have to do to win within the rules or not and don't ever cut an opponent any slack Leo Durocher Willie Mays Babe Ruth Burt Shotton Houston Astros San Francisco Giants St. Louis Cardinals Chuck Dressen Atlanta Braves Ty Cobb October 25 in baseball Harry Dalton Detroit Tigers Dixie Walker Baseball slang Casey Stengel Playoff Satchel Paige Reggie Jackson Los Angeles Dodgers Tris Speaker Baseball statistics Jim Thorpe Philadelphia Phillies Chris Berman Dick Williams Alex Rodriguez Time Out of Mind Florida Marlins Mario Superstar Baseball Harry Walker Whitey Lockman New York Mets Baseball Hall of Fame balloting, 1945 Chicago Cubs New York Yankees Rub__n G__mez Moe Berg Johnny Keane Theory of conduct Connie Mack (baseball) Troms__ I.L. Duke Snider Rickey Henderson Cleveland Indians Dick Allen Humphrey Bogart October 23 in baseball October 7 in baseball Steven Wright Curse of the Bambino Rocky Marciano Lou Boudreau Montreal Canadiens Professional wrestling slang Chicago White Sox Portsmouth F.C. History of Test cricket (1884 to 1889) Sydney Riot of 1879 Treaty of Nice Baseball Hall of Fame balloting, 1946 Curse of the Billy Goat Hal Trosky West Bromwich Albion F.C. Super Bowl XXVI Pet Sounds Pedro Mart__nez Jargon File Fernando Alonso National Football League Lore Cincinnati Reds Big Brother (USA TV series) Miami Dolphins Chess strategy and tactics Milwaukee Brewers Texas Rangers (baseball) Sandy Koufax Sabermetrics United Airlines Flight 93 2005 World Series Cleveland Browns Lucha libre Super Bowl XXI Baseball Ice hockey Oakland Athletics Andrew Dice Clay Pittsburgh Steelers Leon White R.S.C. Anderlecht Seattle Mariners Ichiro Suzuki Ocean's Twelve Expert system 2004 World Series San Francisco 49ers Chicago Blackhawks Tag team The Apprentice 